title: Is Grand Theft Auto 6 Releasing In 2024?
description:
Whether Grand Theft Auto 6 adheres to the expectations of every single fan also remains to be seen. 

But it's been too long since Rockstar has released a new title in the franchise, much less a new triple-A title. A perfect storm is brewing, and we can't wait to see what the next generation of Grand Theft Auto delivers.

title: 15 BEST Single Player Games on Xbox Series X You NEED TO PLAY
description:
While the Xbox Series X's library of single player experiences isn't currently on the same level as that of the PS5 (or the Switch, though that is, of course, a much older console), it's not something to scoff at either. In the two and a half years since its launch, Microsoft's current-gen console has seen a number of excellent single player releases, and the library it has built up to this point has no shortage of gems. 

Here, we're going to talk about a few of them.

title: Planet of Lana Review - The Final Verdict
description:
Overall, Planet of Lana is a beautiful experience with tight gameplay, a compelling and well-designed world, and a strong narrative anchored by two likeable leads and an imposing threat. 

This year – heck, even this quarter – could see it fall under the radar of some big blockbusters. However, the odyssey of Lana and Mui is worth undertaking and remembering.
